name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForCerebrovascularDiseases
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Cerebrovascular Diseases
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to cerebrovascular diseases.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes acute (e.g., cerebrovascular accident) and chronic (e.g., Moyamoya disease) cerebrovascular diseases.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes sequela or complications of cerebrovascular accident, intraoperative and postprocedural cerebrovascular accidents.)
